            "reviews": "“Escape Goat does a bang-up job of providing those all-important &quot;a-ha!&quot; moments of satisfaction, when you solve a puzzle, or get the timing of some jumps just right, and manage finally to complete an area. That's what keeps you playing right through to the end.”<br>8/10 – <a href=\"http://www.ign.com/articles/2012/06/26/escape-goat-review\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >IGN</a><br><br>“… incredibly fun puzzle platformer with a rockin’ soundtrack.”<br><a href=\"http://www.destructoid.com/escape-goat-is-double-jumping-to-pc-226941.phtml\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Destructoid</a><br><br>“With the ability to tackle levels at your own pace, and some masterfully-tuned difficulty, we can guarantee that you’ve never played a better goat-centric game.”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=http://www.gamesradar.com/escape-goat-preview-indie-max-puzzle-platformer/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >GamesRadar</a><br>",
